1 unit Sweet Kale Salad Kit
2 unit Honey Butter Corn Bread

Empty contents of salad kit into a large bowl; drizzle with as much Caesar dressing as you like, then toss to evenly coat.

Serve with Honey Butter Cornbread on the side. (If desired, preheat oven to 350 degrees. Bake corn bread until warmed, 3-5 minutes.)